#1177
@@dThe Broken Paddock@@N~
@@dThe paddock fence has been smashed outward rather than in, and the posts lean away
from whatever made the breach. The paddock ground is churned deep by hooves and shows
the tracks of several large animals. At the south end, a hayrick has been demolished
and the straw scattered and matted down to form a rough nest. Fresh bones, mostly
livestock but a few distinctly human-shaped, are scattered around the perimeter. The
woods press close on the west side and things move in them just beyond visibility.@@N
