than the corridor. Inside, the furniture has been stacked against the interior walls
with great force. The window has been sealed from inside using furniture, clothing,
and what appears to be every book that was in the room. Despite these precautions,
something has clearly been in here since: there are tracks in the dust on the furniture,
small and many-toed, circling the central stack in tight orbits.@@N
