@@dThe Distillation Outbuilding@@N~
@@dThe stone outbuilding smells overwhelmingly of something sweet that makes the eyes
water, and the copper alembics and tubing crowd every surface. The process underway
here has been running without supervision for some time: one vessel has cracked and
