#1206
@@dThe Deep Cave - Crystal Heart@@N~
@@dThis chamber lies directly beneath the root tomb, and the roots themselves have
descended through cracks in the cave ceiling to hang in long pale tendrils here. A
single formation of crystal at the room's center is larger than all the others: man-
height, broadly humanoid in outline, and lit from within by a cold pulsing glow that
the crystal walls of the chamber multiply into something almost blinding. The floor
around the formation is perfectly clean, as if swept constantly by something unseen.
The temperature here is profoundly cold.@@N
