#1168
crypt guardian bone~
@@da Bone Crypt Guardian@@N~
@@da Bone Crypt Guardian stands vigil among the sarcophagi.
@@N
~
@@dThe bone crypt guardian is assembled rather than animated, which may be a philosophical
distinction but is not a practical one. It is four meters of articulated skeleton,
assembled from the contents of several hundred separate interments, and it has been
here long enough that the bones have fused at the joints. Its movement is precise
and economical. It does not react to things that do not come between it and its
charges, and the things it guards are the sarcophagi, which is all it has ever been
asked to do.@@N
~
