#1169
shade mire deep~
@@da Deep Mire Shade@@N~
@@da Deep Mire Shade rises from the water here, dark and cold.
@@N
~
@@dThe deep mire shade is older than the mire, which formed around it when the thornwood
grew thick enough to shadow the low ground. It is the shadow of something that was
never alive, and the cold it carries is the cold of a world without light. Water
moves away from it. It does not interact with physical objects in any ordinary sense
but can affect those that attempt to cross through it in deeply unpleasant ways.@@N
~
