#1170
thornwood cultist elder~
@@dan Elder Thornwood Cultist@@N~
@@dan Elder Thornwood Cultist presides here, eyes closed, hands open.
@@N
~
@@dThe elder cultist came to the thornwood decades ago and has been transfigured by those
decades in ways that are no longer reversible and arguably no longer entirely tragic
from the cultist's own perspective. The thorn-pattern tattoos have been augmented by
actual thorns that have grown through the skin, and the cultist wears them proudly.
Their ritual tools are of extraordinary quality and great age. They are in a state
of deep trance during which they are still entirely capable of extreme violence.@@N
~
