#1171
estate knight thorn blackened~
@@da Blackened Thorn Knight@@N~
@@da Blackened Thorn Knight advances, its armor smoking at the joints.
@@N
~
@@dThis is what an estate thorn knight becomes under the thornwood's fullest influence.
The armor has been completely overtaken: briars have fused the joints solid and new
joints have formed in other places, giving the knight a silhouette that is unsettling
to track. The briars are flowering, which they should not be in this season or this
darkness. The flowers are black and smell of old graves. The knight moves with a
patience that suggests it has all the time that there is.@@N
~
