#1173
revenant lord estate~
@@dLord Harren, the Estate Revenant@@N~
@@dLord Harren, the Estate Revenant, stands before you, the thorn motif of the estate branded on his brow.
@@N
~
@@dThis is the master of the estate, returned. Whatever arrangement Lord Harren made with
the thornwood before his death, this is the fulfillment of it: he stands in the hall
he built, wearing the face he had in life, with the estate's full history in his memory
and the thornwood's full interest behind his eyes. He is articulate and deliberate
and entirely without mercy. The briars at his feet are still growing.@@N
~
