#1174
hunt hound shadow~
@@da Shadow Hunt Hound@@N~
@@da Shadow Hunt Hound paces here, its paws leaving prints of frost.
@@N
~
@@dThe shadow hunt hound runs with the wild hunt and exists between kills in a state that
is more concept than creature. When given form it has the shape of a very large,
very lean hound, the color of deep shadow, with white-ringed eyes. Its breath is cold
enough to frost the air at all temperatures. It is utterly silent until it is not.@@N
~
