#1175
estate bone soldier~
@@dan Estate Bone Soldier@@N~
@@dan Estate Bone Soldier marches here with an unhurried precision.
@@N
~
@@dThe bone soldiers are the thornwood estate's lowest-ranking undead garrison: individual
skeletons fitted with the estate's house guard armor and armed with weapons from the
armory, all of it now brown with age and patchy with the moss that has grown in the
sheltered hollows of the kit. They move in silence, patrol assigned routes, and do not
deviate. Their eyes have a dull orange light in the sockets, like an ember in old ash.@@N
~
