#1176
thornwood shaman~
@@da Thornwood Shaman@@N~
@@da Thornwood Shaman chants here, its voice braided with thorns.
@@N
~
@@dThe shaman is the ritual specialist of the thornwood cult, a step above the ordinary
cultist and several steps in a direction the ordinary cultist has not yet imagined.
The thorn integration in their body is so complete that the briars now constitute
their circulatory system, their sap visible through the skin in fine dark lines. They
speak in a voice that carries harmonics outside the human range. They are communing
with the thornwood directly at all times. Their attention is not fully here.@@N
~
