#1177
wight barrow elder~
@@dan Elder Barrow Wight@@N~
@@dan Elder Barrow Wight emerges here, burial goods still clasped in its hands.
@@N
~
@@dThe elder barrow wight is one of the oldest undead in the thornwood, interred here
before the estate was built and before the thornwood had its current character. It
has adapted, as old things do: the burial goods it carries have been transformed by
the same processes that transformed it, and what were once offerings of bronze and
ceramic are now objects of dark significance. It does not acknowledge the existence
of the living as a category.@@N
~
