#1178
spirit deep cave~
@@da Deep Cave Spirit@@N~
@@da Deep Cave Spirit moves through the crystal here, barely distinguishable from the light.
@@N
~
@@dThe deep cave spirit is ancient and has no truck with the concerns of the surface world.
It is composed of whatever it is that occupies very old, very still places: concentrated
presence without form, existing as a distortion in the light of the crystal cave. It is
not hostile by intent, but the intense cold that surrounds it causes significant harm to
living creatures that spend time in its vicinity, and it does not move away from them.@@N
~
