#1179
crystal lich thornwood~
@@dThe Thornwood Lich@@N~
@@dThe Thornwood Lich rises from its throne here, cold fire crackling at its fingertips.
@@N
~
@@dThe figure on the throne in the sealed chamber is the thornwood's architect: the
scholar-lord who designed the binding in the cave below and bound themselves into the
estate to sustain it. They have been here for centuries, which is long enough to become
something that the word lich does not fully describe. They wear the estate's formal
dress, now fused to the form beneath it. They remember every room, every name, every
choice, and the weight of that memory is visible in the stillness with which they regard
you. They are the thornwood's heart and the thornwood is their body.@@N
~
